44:01.819 --> 44:03.139
mnaona bei ni ghali sana

44:03.139 --> 44:03.940
bado tunaweza kujadili

44:06.139 --> 44:07.100
bado tunaweza kujadili

44:07.860 --> 44:08.699
Kwa ufahamu wangu,

44:08.819 --> 44:09.619
katika eneo hili letu,

44:09.619 --> 44:11.139
nyumba zenye ukubwa na mpangilio sawa,

44:11.500 --> 44:12.819
kodi yake ni kama

44:12.819 --> 44:13.819
elfu kumi na nane hivi,

44:16.540 --> 44:18.659
sasa hii nyumba,

44:18.659 --> 44:20.259
mwenye nyumba yuko nje ya nchi kwa muda mrefu,

44:20.460 --> 44:21.619
hizi vifaa na vyombo vya nyumbani,

44:22.020 --> 44:23.339
kama hazitumiwi kwa muda mrefu,

44:23.339 --> 44:24.020
zinaweza kuharibika haraka,

44:24.299 --> 44:25.779
hivyo mpangazi kwa kweli

44:25.940 --> 44:26.940
anahifadhi nyumba

44:27.819 --> 44:28.699
Bei imewekwa chini

44:28.699 --> 44:29.500
Pia ni busara

44:30.259 --> 44:30.860
Nimeelewa

44:31.619 --> 44:32.699
Sawa, asante kwa mchango wako

44:32.860 --> 44:33.779
Baadaye nikihitaji

44:33.779 --> 44:34.540
Nitaungana nawe tena

44:36.900 --> 44:37.500
Binti Ruan

44:37.580 --> 44:37.980
Asante

44:37.980 --> 44:39.179
Kama una wasiwasi wowote

44:39.179 --> 44:40.219
Unaweza kutuambia

44:40.819 --> 44:41.500
Hakuna hakuna, Binti Ruan

44:41.819 --> 44:42.420
Nitaangalia tena

44:42.819 --> 44:43.619
Kaka

44:44.420 --> 44:45.179
Mwakili anasema

44:45.299 --> 44:46.739
Mteja hakupenda hata moja

44:48.179 --> 44:49.219
Umechagua nyumba za aina gani

44:52.179 --> 44:52.779
Kaka, angalia

44:53.540 --> 44:55.259
Kwa upande wowote, ukarabati wa mazingira ya nyumba

44:55.460 --> 44:57.219
Urefu wa jengo, mwangaza, upepo

44:57.219 --> 44:57.980
Kila kitu nimefanya

44:57.980 --> 44:59.020
Kwa mujibu wa maagizo yako

44:59.500 --> 45:00.339
Nimechagua kwa makini

45:00.339 --> 45:01.179
Hakika zote ni hizi

45:02.139 --> 45:02.699
Nzuri sana

45:02.900 --> 45:04.540
Basi unatoa bei gani?

45:05.020 --> 45:05.699
Elfu nne

45:06.580 --> 45:07.739
Sijui kwa nini

45:08.060 --> 45:08.940
Kuna watu

45:08.940 --> 45:10.460
wanashindwa kupendeza na bei hii

45:10.819 --> 45:11.819
Watu wa sasa wamekuwa vipi?

45:12.179 --> 45:13.299
Wanaona pesa kama takataka?

45:15.779 --> 45:18.540
Basi umekuwa na shida sana

45:19.420 --> 45:20.219
Sio shida, sio shida

45:20.219 --> 45:21.259
Kaka, ni wajibu wangu

45:22.139 --> 45:22.779
Ni wajibu wangu
